' Shared status legend for Nelkinda PlantUML diagrams.

!include status-styles.puml

legend right
|= Marker |= Meaning |
|<STATUS_PROPOSED_COLOR> <<proposed>> | Proposed / under consideration |
|<STATUS_APPROVED_COLOR> <<approved>> | Approved / not yet implemented |
|<STATUS_IMPLEMENTED_COLOR> <<implemented>> | Implemented and current |
|<STATUS_DEPRECATED_COLOR> <<deprecated>> | Deprecated / avoid for new work |
endlegend
